Package com.cornell.opencomm.client

Class Summary
XMPPClient Main Android Activity Class for the XMPPClient implementation.
XMPPClientLogger Simple class that handles constants related to the logging infrastructure
XMPPClientSettings Dialog to get the inputs from the user to log in to a Jabber server.
XMPPInvitationReceivedDialog Handles the processing of the event where an invite to a MUC chat session is received
XMPPInviteDialog Simple Dialog to enable a user to invite another user to join a MUC chat room
XMPPLogOff Simple Dialog to enable a logged in user to log off from the Jabber session.
XMPPRoomCreateDialog Simple Dialog to create a MultiUserChat room
